entry.def: Aries is one of the twelve signs of the zodiac. Its symbol is a ram. People who are born approximately between 21st March and 19th April come under this sign.

entry.def: An Aries is a person whose sign of the zodiac is Aries.

means.word_mean: 1. (astrology) a person who is born while the sun is in Aries
2. a small zodiacal constellation in the northern hemisphere; between Pisces and Taurus
3. the first sign of the zodiac which the sun enters at the vernal equinox; the sun is in this sign from about March 21 to April 19
